OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGove says lax rules partly 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto blame for Grenfell      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Flawed government guidance on building 
OL,6, standards was partly to blame for the  
OL,7, Grenfell Tower fire, Housing Secretary 
OL,8, Michael Gove has said.                 
OL,10,FHe believes the system of regulation   
OL,11,Fwas "faulty and ambiguous" and not     
OL,12,Fpoliced properly by the government.    
OL,14,FMr Gove said there was also an "active 
OL,15,Fwillingness" on the part of developers 
OL,16,Fto endanger lives for profit.          
OL,18,FThe inquiry into the 2017 fire - in    
OL,19,Fwhich 72 people died - has closed and  
OL,20,Fis expected to report later this year. 
